<div dir="ltr">do you use IB as a transport? max message size in IB/RDMA  is limited to 2G, but OMPI 1.7 splits large buffers during RDMA into 2G chunks.<div><br></div></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><br><div class="gmail_quote">
